Remarks. A new record to Angola (
Fig. 3 A
). This large-sized subspecies is present throughout South Africa (Transvaal), Mozambique , Zimbabwe and Zambia (Werner 2000 b). The two specimens from Angola are similar to the ones figured in Werner ( 2000 b, p. 35 , Figs 218 a, 218 a- 1 ). The type of habitat where the specimens were taken is unknown.

